Kugla korupcije

Orb of Corruption is a conglomerate of moving iridescent glass. It envelops the item while the ritual is ongoing. After completing the ritual, it shatters into colorful glass pieces.

You can use the orb to perform a 1 hour ritual. In order to perform a ritual, you need to be in a place of high Underdark > Faerzress source. When you do so, choose a magic item to unpredictably modify. Roll on the Corruption table to determine the outcome. Only items of very rare rarity and below can be corrupted. Once an item is corrupted, it cannot be corrupted again.

Corruption table

d6 Outcome
1 Nothing happens
2 The item becomes Soulbound
3 The rarity of the item increases by 1 (maximum of legendary)
4 The rarity of the item decreases by 1 (minimum of common)
5 If the item increases your AC, it increases it by -1, otherwise if it increases your damage, it increases it by -1, otherwise if the item has charges, it gains a -1 charge
6 If the item increases your AC, it increases it by +1, otherwise if it increases your damage, it increases it by +1, otherwise if the item has charges, it gains a +1 charge

U priči

Magični predmet koji su numerijanski znanstvenici koristili u procesu korumpiranja drugih magičnih predmeta.

Jedna ova kugla nalazila se u numerijanskoj postaji koji su naši heroji otkrili u 35. sessionu. U idućem sessionu smo je i "posudili".

Kugla je uništena kada ju je u 37. sessionu Gundam iskoristio na Ledinom bodežu.
